Description: Provides object-oriented classes and utilities for representing, 
    manipulating, and analyzing three-dimensional molecular structures. 
    The core 'Molecule3D' class stores atomic coordinates, bonds, and anchors 
    for positioning molecules, while the 'SymAxis' class represents proper 
    rotational symmetry axes (Câ‚™). Includes functionality for reading Tripos MOL2 
    files, geometric transformations, anchor manipulation, and integration with 
    cheminformatics toolkits for coordinate-based modeling.
